{
  "widgets": [
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Dev API 5xx-Rate (%)",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "region": "eu-central-1",
        "period": 300,
        "stat": "Sum",
        "metrics": [
          [
            "swisstopo/dev-api",
            "Http5xxCount",
            {
              "id": "m5",
              "label": "Http5xxCount"
            }
          ],
          [
            ".",
            "HttpRequestCount",
            {
              "id": "mt",
              "label": "HttpRequestCount"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "expression": "IF(mt>=20,(m5/mt)*100,0)",
              "id": "er",
              "label": "Http5xxRatePercent"
            }
          ]
        ],
        "annotations": {
          "horizontal": [
            {
              "label": "Warn >= 2%",
              "value": 2,
              "color": "#f59e0b"
            },
            {
              "label": "Kritisch >= 5%",
              "value": 5,
              "color": "#ef4444"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Dev API p95 Latenz (TargetResponseTime)",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "region": "eu-central-1",
        "period": 60,
        "stat": "p95",
        "metrics": [
          [
            "AWS/ApplicationELB",
            "TargetResponseTime",
            "LoadBalancer",
            "${LOAD_BALANCER_DIMENSION}",
            "TargetGroup",
            "${TARGET_GROUP_DIMENSION}",
            {
              "label": "TargetResponseTime p95"
            }
          ]
        ],
        "annotations": {
          "horizontal": [
            {
              "label": "Warn >= 1.2s",
              "value": 1.2,
              "color": "#f59e0b"
            },
            {
              "label": "Kritisch >= 2.5s",
              "value": 2.5,
              "color": "#ef4444"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 6,
      "width": 24,
      "height": 4,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "**Zeitfenster-Filter:** 15m und 1h (CloudWatch Dashboard \u201eCustom\u201c: `-PT15M` und `-PT1H`).\\n\\n**Oncall-Startwerte:**\\n- 5xx-Rate: Warn >= 2%, Kritisch >= 5% (nur wenn `HttpRequestCount >= 20/5m`)\\n- p95-Latenz: Warn >= 1.2s, Kritisch >= 2.5s"
      }
    }
  ]
}
